## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in the selected materials. The perspectives included are primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global views on abortion. Additionally, the complexity of individual beliefs means that not all nuances of the anti-abortion stance are captured. Further research could explore a broader range of cultural and religious contexts to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.